name: Kabosu Inu
public_notice: Kabosu Inu (KABOSU INU) has migrated from their older contract to a new one. For more information, please view this announcement on Twitter.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Kabosu Inu is an ERC20 token dedicating appreciation and awareness of Kabosu, the Shiba Inu dog that inspired dogecoin. Kabosu is one of the biggest inspirations in the meme coin world and our community will grow strong to spread awareness of the great Kabosu.
